N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 816.2 - Definitions

State Regulations

As used in this Part, the following words and terms shall
have the stated meaning: (a) Municipality means a county, city, town, or village, but shall not include
those counties contained within the City of New York. (b) Secretary means the New York State

Secretary of State. Notes
